## Naming Conventions

| Artifact | Convention | Example |
|----------|-----------|---------|
| Unit test file | `<subject>.test.<ext>` | `user.service.test.ts` |
| Integration test file | `<subject>.integration.test.<ext>` | `user.repo.integration.test.ts` |
| E2E test file | `<subject>.e2e.<ext>` | `login-flow.e2e.ts` |
| Test suite (`describe`) | Noun phrase matching the unit under test | `"UserService"` |
| Test case (`it`/`test`) | `"should <verb> <condition>"` | `"should return 401 when token is expired"` |
| Test helper/factory | `create<Entity>` or `make<Entity>` | `createUser()`, `makeOrder()` |
| Mock/stub variable | `mock<Dependency>` | `mockUserRepository` |

