## Test Organization

```
<project-root>/
├── src/                          # Source code
│   └── <module>/
│       ├── <module>.service.ts
│       └── <module>.service.test.ts   # Unit tests co-located
├── tests/
│   ├── integration/               # Integration tests
│   │   └── <module>.integration.test.ts
│   └── e2e/                       # End-to-end tests
│       └── <flow>.e2e.ts
└── .qa-report.md                  # Generated by QA agent (gitignored or committed per team preference)
```

---

## CI/CD Integration

- Run unit tests on every push
- Run integration tests on PR and main branch pushes
- Run E2E tests on main branch pushes and release branches
- Publish coverage reports as CI artifacts
- Fail the pipeline if coverage drops below `{{QA_COVERAGE_THRESHOLD}}`
- Post QA agent report as a PR comment when `report_format` includes `markdown`
